<subSubSection lastPageId="558" lastPageNumber="559" pageId="557" pageNumber="558" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="557" pageNumber="558">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph lastPageId="558" lastPageNumber="559" pageId="557" pageNumber="558">
This species ranges from southwestern Pennsylvania to the Mississippi River in western Illinois, south to southeastern Louisiana and southern Alabama 
<pageBreakToken pageId="558" pageNumber="559" start="start">[</pageBreakToken>
see Freitag 1969: Fig. 131]. The record from South Carolina (Kirk 1970: 11; Ciegler 2000: 70) is probably in error.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
